Config tool(1)                  Clam AntiVirus                  Config tool(1)



NAME
       clamconf - Clam AntiVirus configuration utility

SYNOPSIS
       clamconf [options]

DESCRIPTION
       clamconf displays the values of configuration options.

OPTIONS
       -h, --help
              Display help and exit.

       -V, --version
              Display software version and exit.

       -c DIR, --config-dir DIR
              Search  for configuration files clamd.conf and freshclam.conf in
              DIR.

       -n, --non-default
              Only print non-default settings.

       -g CONFIG_NAME, --generate-config=CONFIG_NAME
              Generate example configuration file.

CREDITS
       The idea of this tool is based on Postfix's postconf. clamconf was cre-
       ated under pressure from Tomasz Papszun ;-)

AUTHOR
       Tomasz Kojm <tkojm@clamav.net>

SEE ALSO
       clamd.conf(5), freshclam.conf(5)



